{"tid":1977940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡新增942宗新型冠狀病毒確診個案，再破單日最高增幅紀錄","createTime":"2020-04-18T10:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T18:09:28.000Z","uid":25240,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3f2c84565a1fb0aa795c7227df4e681a022fc35d","tid":1977940,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T10:27:11.000Z","msg":"新加坡目前累計的確診病例達到5992宗，衛生部說新增個案絕大部分是住在外勞宿舍、持有工作許可證的外籍勞工。至於本地確診個案則持續減少，有14名本地公民或永久居民確診染病。<br />\n<br />\n總理李顯龍發帖文說，外勞宿舍的確診病例仍在連日增加，幸好絕大多數患者都是年輕，病情亦輕，醫療團隊會繼續留意他們的健康狀況。他又說未來數日是抗疫關鍵，全國人民應盡一己之力，打敗病毒。<br />\n<br />\n而針對網民批評政府的疫情處理手法，李顯龍的妻子何晶最少兩度在網上發帖文反駁，指全世界都低估了新型冠狀病毒沒有症狀也會傳播的風險，又指出如果有外勞在新加坡染病，新加坡政府會照顧他們，不應該將他們遺送回國。<br />\n<br />\n當局在樟宜展覽中心興建的第二間臨時醫院基本完工，會用來安置輕症及康復中的患者，預計可容納2800名病人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=388163\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388163&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppegxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=a2363043\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388163&h=45c441bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=388163</a>"},{"pid":"d4b48f8987a7a328b4a70825f87fac6f250c6a98","tid":1977940,"uid":11001,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T10:27:41.000Z","msg":"Monkey sick <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511c04eb856033954077d453f79212867b473275","tid":1977940,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T10:28:17.000Z","msg":"monkey together die"},{"pid":"1e3b5c43c95170cbecd79ef936c26b1d277a102a","tid":1977940,"uid":31475,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AfVduYr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAfVduYr.jpg&h=34b19296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n